Title: An Act Changing the Name of Barangay Bongog in the Municipality of Catubig, Province of Northern Samar, to Barangay Domingo Mercader
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 683
An Act Changing the Name of Barangay Bongog in the Municipality of Catubig, Province of Northern Samar, to Barangay Domingo Mercader
Section 1. The name of Barangay Bongog in the Municipality of Catubig, Province of Northern Samar, is changed to Barangay Domingo Mercader.
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Approved: March 7, 1984
